
Hexen II: Hammer of Thyrion
Version 1.4.0

http://uhexen2.sourceforge.net/
http://sourceforge.net/projects/uhexen2/

Hammer of Thyrion is a port of Raven's Hexen II source code to
support Linux, FreeBSD, other unices & Windows. It is based on
the initial linux port Anvil of Thyrion 1.2.0 by Dan Olson and
Clément Bourdarias (http://aot.linuxgames.com), and is patched
by Steven A. and O. Sezer with some additional code taken from
the pa3pyx and jshexen2 source ports.

Hexen II was created by Raven Software Corp.,  published by Id
Software Inc and distributed by Activision, Inc.  Hexen II and
Portal of Praevus are trademarks of Raven Software Corporation.
Hammer of Thyrion is *not* made and is *not* supported by any
of these software companies in any way.

